Class LogicalResourceRow

    • com.espertech.esper.eeutil.domain.push.LogicalResourceRow

  • public class LogicalResourceRow
extends java.lang.Object
    Holder for the different types of logical resources that can be subscribed to. Engine uri is maintained separately to make it easier to obtain.
